Class ApplicationContextsRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.camel.ApplicationContextsRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EventListener, Registry, ApplicationListener<ApplicationContextEvent>, Ordered

    public class ApplicationContextsRegistry
extends Object
implements Registry, ApplicationListener<ApplicationContextEvent>, Ordered
    Implementation Registry that load beans from all ApplicationContexts. For every ApplicationContext is created own ApplicationContextRegistry.

    2.0

    Roman Havlicek
